00:21:47.119 --> 00:21:52.400
And so we're here on a call with a podcast with all three of us have worked on different

00:21:53.520 --> 00:21:58.560
lazy expression systems for data frames. And so I think that's maybe the first time I've been,

00:21:58.560 --> 00:22:02.800
maybe it would be nice if Philip Cloud was here and maybe Matthew Rockland, we would have

00:22:03.520 --> 00:22:10.079
a whole group full of intermediate representation expression system fanatics.

