want to be entertained. And all data science popular projects seem to be named after animals.

00:29:10.800 --> 00:29:16.000
So I looked on the Wikipedia page on the list of animals that had not yet been taken,

00:29:16.000 --> 00:29:19.599
and I found Puffin. Seems like the perfect name, but unfortunately,

00:29:19.599 --> 00:29:24.800
there was already a Python package called Puffin. And then I found Nowells, which immediately

00:29:24.800 --> 00:29:30.160
reminded me of that viral Mr. Weeble song about Nowells. And I thought, I can't call it this.

