roll Narwhals in. And I do feel like it really gassed them up to just have you there,

00:36:06.399 --> 00:36:12.879
break things down, and even explain how Narwhals could do the things that they asked to have that

00:36:12.879 --> 00:36:19.439
answered so fast was, I feel like, really impressive to just have the person on a call

00:36:19.439 --> 00:36:26.159
kind of like clearing the path. Thank you. I think people, sometimes people

